wsdl:operation.name: Login
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns a security token for use with the other service functions. You'll need an API-key and a valid account. Token remains valid for 24 hours.

wsdl:operation.name: LoginBytoken
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Re-initialise Session object.

wsdl:operation.name: SaveCredentials
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Save the login credentials in a cookie.

wsdl:operation.name: DeleteCredentials
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Remove the cookie with the login credentials.

wsdl:operation.name: CreateUser

wsdl:operation.name: CreateContact
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates a new contact with the specified emailaddress.

wsdl:operation.name: CreateCall
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates a new call with the specified flow and returns its ID.

wsdl:operation.name: CreateCallEx
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Creates a new call with the specified document and extra data, and returns its ID.

wsdl:operation.name: SetCallValues
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Set values of the fields defined in the flow of the specified call.

wsdl:operation.name: GetCallValues
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Get values of the fields used in the flow of the specified call.

wsdl:operation.name: SetChatMessage
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Sends a chat text to the server.

wsdl:operation.name: GetDocumentCursor
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns current cursor position over document from the server.

wsdl:operation.name: SetDocumentCursor
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Sends current cursor position over document to the server.

wsdl:operation.name: SetRedirectURL
